<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>443</hymn_number>
<author>Lalthangpuia</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Et chimloh pakcha din mi a pieng hi,
 Pawm chim puong ie, kipak zing ka;
 Pawmlai vawnsen cha hi.

[V2]
 Damsawt ta hen, zuo minlun chawian din,
 Khang in, hung lien meng hen la Aw;
 Lal sepaih gal do di'n,
 Zion galthuom mangin Lalpa,
 Vang hun pien Aw.

[V3]
 2. Chun-leh-zuo vawnchawih in ei nem pen ie,
 Phungguol namtin kipahna chuh;
 Vawnsen hung pieng cha hi.

[V4]
 3. Awi ing ie, zaila leh chu'n thehnem in,
 Ka saulun sung dung leh vaiah;
 Vawnsen pakbang chawi ka.

[V5]
 4. Sietlei leh Thangvan a ka zuo Minlun,
 Na min pak bangin chawi ingka;
 Vawnsen paibang kuoh hi.</lyrics>
<title>GIVE HIM LONG LIFE</title>
</song>